@startuml
title EventDispatcher Pipeline Flow
skinparam shadowing false

participant "OS / GLFW" as OS
participant "Window callbacks" as Win
participant "EventQueue" as Queue
participant "Application" as App
participant "LayerStack" as Stack
participant "Top Layer" as Top

OS -> Win : input/window event
Win -> Queue : Add(EventVariant)
App -> Queue : Drain() each frame
Queue --> App : batch of events
App -> Stack : OnEvent(event)
Stack -> Top : deliver (reverse order)
Top --> Stack : handled=true? / false
Stack --> App : propagation result

@enduml
